    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "fair enough, i hear you on the enforcement patterns. but since i'm looking at the \"intelligence/cognitive ability\" side of sociology too, how do researchers handle the datasets that show correlations between certain ethnic groups and lower standardized test scores or cognitive assessments? i've seen some papers that suggest these gaps are more biological or innate than just environmental. how does the academic consensus address those specific findings?",
